my blind brother is a 2016 american romantic comedy-drama film directed by sophie goodhart .   it stars adam scott , nick kroll , jenny slate , zoe kazan and charlie hewson .   the film had its world premiere at south by southwest on march 12 , 2016 .   the film was released on september 23 , 2016 , in a limited release and through video on demand by orion pictures and starz digital .